cdata.name: Paygine
cdata.desc:
Paygine is a cryptocurrency financial platform based on Best2Pay company processing center. Using an automatic crypto-to-fiat conversion system, it provides the users (businesses and customers) with the tools to deal with cryptocurrency as their ordinary currency. Paygine features the possibility to maintain wallets in both fiat and cryptocurrencies, and convert funds between them as well as to transact cryptocurrency to and from a bank card. 

The PGC token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It will act as the basic functional tool to the Paygine users, allowing them to have 10% to 30% discount when using the PGC token to pay for goods and services.
